Lesley Dunlop https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lesley_Dunlop 0 Lesley Jane Dunlop (born 10 March 1956 in Newcastle upon Tyne) is an English actress. She is best known for her roles as Anna Kirkwall in Where the Heart Is, Zoë Angell in May to December and her current role as Brenda Walker in Emmerdale.
